'''Lizard-ants''' were native creatures from the once run-down [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Anoat/Legends|Anoat]] that lived in hives. During their mating season the creatures' behavior would change and they would become extremely active and swarm. The species had six legs.

[[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] had once kept a few lizard-ants as exotic pets.

